Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.71,0:00:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,有名格斗家把人妻带回去中出NTR\N菅野真穗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.08,0:00:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,真穗，开始咯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.01,0:00:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.40,0:00:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.40,0:00:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.33,0:00:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,赢了，太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.36,0:00:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是内藤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.36,0:00:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.43,0:00:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么先看啦\N我叫你好几次了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.25,0:01:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,内藤嬴了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.25,0:01:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,当然啦，超帅的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.25,0:01:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,真的？好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.25,0:01:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不块是常胜冠军内藤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.85,0:01:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,好想看唷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.31,0:01:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,谁叫你这么慢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.50,0:01:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,现在是访问
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.60,0:01:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,隔了一年的胜利，感觉如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.80,0:01:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然隔了一年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.81,0:01:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但能证明自己多强，还是很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.21,0:01:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好帅唷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.21,0:01:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,妻子跟我都是内藤的粉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.21,0:01:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,他是我们的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.93,0:01:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,内藤是我们的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.56,0:01:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不管遇到什么困难
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.83,0:01:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,内藤都会再站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.36,0:02:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我们看了非常感动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.82,0:02:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.35,0:02:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.91,0:02:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是内藤的感想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.23,0:02:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,内藤！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.30,0:02:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,果然!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.73,0:02:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我是你的粉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.81,0:02:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,比赛也看了，好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.45,0:02:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.25,0:02:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,可以握手吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.11,0:02:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在练习\N没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.68,0:02:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.50,0:02:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,可以拍照吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.83,0:03:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以\N没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.83,0:03:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.21,0:03:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.88,0:03:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,可以上传到SNS吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.18,0:03:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,可以唷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.95,0:03:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.98,0:03:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.56,0:03:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的遇到了内藤？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.40,0:03:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.76,0:03:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.96,0:03:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,车站前的公园
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.95,0:03:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好好唷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.11,0:03:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,内藤看起来如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.21,0:03:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,很壮喔，还很帅喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.08,0:03:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,没跟他要签名吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.71,0:03:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他在练习耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.61,0:03:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,都拍照了就签名嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.68,0:04:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.13,0:04:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,下次把他带回家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.26,0:04:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,说我是粉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.76,0:04:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啦\N为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.86,0:04:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,可以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.86,0:04:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啦，他很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.26,0:04:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好想被内藤打打看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.45,0:04:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.11,0:04:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,带他回家嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.48,0:04:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.41,0:04:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好好\N很棒吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.01,0:05:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我是内藤，我看到你的SNS了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.41,0:05:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,内藤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.68,0:05:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.75,0:05:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的是内藤？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.10,0:05:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我是本人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.46,0:05:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,突然联络你，吓到了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.26,0:05:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉，我吓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.28,0:05:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你上次跟我照相
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.31,0:05:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫真穗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.18,0:05:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你住河边附近吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.40,0:05:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.96,0:05:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我早上十点都在那练习
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.30,0:05:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,下次帮你签名吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.76,0:06:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,真的？我老公很想要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.61,0:06:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你结婚啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.68,0:06:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊，帮你签两份吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.85,0:06:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.25,0:06:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,请帮我签名
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.18,0:06:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.03,0:06:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,来\N谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.88,0:07:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,再见\N加油
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.70,0:07:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我练习结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.21,0:07:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.28,0:07:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你的签名
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.61,0:07:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以帮我打扫房间吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.36,0:08:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,打扫？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.35,0:08:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不行吧？抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.18,0:08:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我房间很乱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.55,0:08:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,才会这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.80,0:08:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,可以喔，我下午有空
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.40,0:08:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,请让我帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.61,0:09:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我回来了\N欢迎回家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.73,0:09:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么这么开心？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.13,0:09:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.73,0:09:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,内藤的签名？怎么弄到的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.85,0:09:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,快说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.71,0:09:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我把照片传到SNS上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.48,0:09:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,他就联络我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.98,0:09:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,帮我签名
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.05,0:09:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,太猛了\N真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.90,0:09:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,对吧？\N也让我联络内藤嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.26,0:09:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.03,0:09:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.83,0:09:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,拿到内藤的签名
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.95,0:09:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,内藤还要我帮他打扫房间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.25,0:10:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,打扫？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.95,0:10:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,他问我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.95,0:10:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,内藤的房间？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.05,0:10:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,他说房间很乱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.30,0:10:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,没有人帮忙打扫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.30,0:10:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你想去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.00,0:10:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,他说会给钱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.83,0:10:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不用啦，免费去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.16,0:10:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.18,0:10:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,当然可以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.51,0:10:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,然后带他回我们家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.61,0:10:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.35,0:10:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,去问他爱吃什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.98,0:10:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,还有爱喝什么酒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.30,0:10:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好想和他成为好友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.50,0:10:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.06,0:10:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,要走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.76,0:10:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,等等，来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.40,0:11:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你今天要去内藤房间？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.48,0:11:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.31,0:11:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,要和他成为好友喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.35,0:11:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，只是打扫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.08,0:11:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一家要跟内藤成为好友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.05,0:11:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啦\N可以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.83,0:11:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不行\N可以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.60,0:11:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,那我走了，拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.30,0:11:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你好，来得太早了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.60,0:12:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.55,0:12:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.28,0:12:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？\N抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.08,0:12:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我好紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.68,0:12:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,很乱吧，失望了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.48,0:12:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不会啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.83,0:12:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我开始了\N拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.76,0:13:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你休息吧，很累吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.10,0:13:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.16,0:14:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么时候开始当我粉丝的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.50,0:14:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,一开始就是唷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.53,0:14:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,从你的出道战开始
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.73,0:14:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,, 我跟先生约会去看的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.58,0:14:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,约会看这，真稀奇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.15,0:14:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,先生约你的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.51,0:14:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他一直强硬要我去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.55,0:14:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,说非去不可
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,可是真的很棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.03,0:14:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你来打扫也没关系啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.00,0:14:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不是粉丝会回绝吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.36,0:14:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.73,0:15:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.53,0:15:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.18,0:15:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.68,0:15:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,想让我操吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.05,0:15:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,说什么啊？粉丝会生气唷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.06,0:15:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我是很认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.86,0:16:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,别逗我了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.98,0:16:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.38,0:16:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.01,0:16:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢我吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.81,0:16:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.01,0:16:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.43,0:16:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你是我的粉丝吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.40,0:16:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,可以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.40,0:16:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.73,0:16:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你可是英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.46,0:16:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.35,0:16:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,做爱跟运动一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.01,0:16:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,, 不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.31,0:16:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.85,0:16:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.15,0:16:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.80,0:16:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.76,0:17:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以\N做爱跟运动一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.33,0:17:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.48,0:17:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我对你一见钟情了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.28,0:17:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.05,0:17:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.71,0:17:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.23,0:17:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,干什么？\N快摸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.58,0:17:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.91,0:17:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,很热呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.08,0:17:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你也,兴奋了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.55,0:17:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.03,0:18:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.23,0:18:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.88,0:18:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.36,0:18:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.58,0:18:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.01,0:19:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱上你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.86,0:19:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不.可能
