Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.18,0:46:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.33,0:46:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你常对粉丝出手吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.83,0:46:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,她们可都是自愿的
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.35,0:47:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,想见我就来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.95,0:47:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会再来了
