Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.38,0:47:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,回来啦，如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.95,0:47:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么在家？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.85,0:48:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我提早回来，结果怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.20,0:48:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.53,0:48:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我只有打扫。没了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.06,0:48:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么？应该聊个天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.35,0:48:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他要训练，很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.31,0:48:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.35,0:48:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.15,0:48:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,还想跟他做朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.50,0:48:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这种机会不多唷
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.60,0:48:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.40,0:48:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我好期待
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.23,0:48:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,下次告诉他我是粉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.21,0:48:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,顺便请他来吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.28,0:49:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,说不定没有下次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.21,0:49:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,是唷
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.15,0:49:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我还提早回家
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.96,0:49:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.35,0:49:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.38,0:50:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要去看内藤的比赛？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.21,0:50:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,之前太忙了，都没空去
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.91,0:50:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这次我会去抢票
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.35,0:50:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这次比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.33,0:50:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,一起去现场看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.33,0:50:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,说不定他这次会输唷
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.40,0:50:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他一定会赢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.73,0:50:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我准备好去抢票了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.91,0:50:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好期待
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.51,0:50:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,顺便买些周边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.31,0:50:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.78,0:50:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好期待唷
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.70,0:50:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好想快点看
