Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.70,1:08:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.33,1:08:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.15,1:09:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我先走了，记得锁门喔
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.55,1:09:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,真穗，我没袜子穿了
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.40,1:09:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,没有袜子\N在衣柜啊
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.46,1:09:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,没有耶\N有啦
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.63,1:09:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你有这种内衣？
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.83,1:09:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是只穿白色的吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.65,1:10:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,朋友送的啦
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.78,1:10:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我拿袜子给你
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.46,1:10:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,现在要播内藤的训练画面
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.90,1:10:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,要播内藤的画面了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.98,1:10:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我很忙
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.18,1:10:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,是喔
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.48,1:10:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我等等看
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.86,1:10:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你最近有联络内藤吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.80,1:11:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,打扫之后还有吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.08,1:11:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,他很忙的
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.75,1:11:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，也是啦
