Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.70,1:11:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好猛喔
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.46,1:11:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,快来看
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.36,1:11:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.13,1:11:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,快看嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.68,1:11:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,请内藤说句话
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.85,1:11:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,开始访问了，快看
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.55,1:11:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,请说说现在的心情
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.13,1:11:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.76,1:12:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我会努力调整身体
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.13,1:12:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,努力比赛
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.28,1:12:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,到最后一刻
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.85,1:12:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.88,1:12:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好短喔
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.63,1:12:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我去买菜了\N慢走
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.88,1:12:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,慢走
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.58,1:12:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好，就这样
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.31,1:13:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,之后麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.76,1:13:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,内藤只要再赢一场
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.76,1:13:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,就可以进决赛
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.28,1:13:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我的英雄不可能输
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.88,1:13:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他一定会赢
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.28,1:13:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.00,1:13:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,又瞒着老公来啦？
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.36,1:13:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,当然瞒着他
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.91,1:13:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,老婆让我玩了，他会开心吧？\N是我的铁粉呢
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.88,1:13:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能啦
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.68,1:14:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,下次比赛加油
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.81,1:14:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这边就麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.58,1:15:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,爽吗？\N好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.90,1:15:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不要拍
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.10,1:15:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不会外流啦
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.26,1:16:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,, 不要拍啦
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.28,1:16:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题的，继续
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.55,1:16:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以给别人看哦
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.13,1:16:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不会啦
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.83,1:16:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,看着我
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.76,1:16:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.18,1:17:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.88,1:17:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,继续，好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.10,1:18:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,用力点，去了
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.63,1:18:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.91,1:18:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好多
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.55,1:18:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.41,1:18:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你老公也是粉丝呢
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.95,1:19:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他有看我的报道？
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.51,1:19:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,有
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.85,1:19:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,把影片传给他吧
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.70,1:19:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.70,1:19:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,说好不外流的吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.63,1:19:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那当收藏吧
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.70,1:19:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,真火大
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.28,1:19:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,一个月后的比赛结束再联络你
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.25,1:19:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这么久？
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.51,1:19:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我得练习
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.65,1:19:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.78,1:19:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我去练习了
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.38,1:20:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.18,1:20:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.78,1:20:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,赢了
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.81,1:20:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.96,1:20:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,太帅了
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.76,1:20:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,好强唷
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.60,1:20:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好猛
Dialogue: 0,1:20:26.63,1:20:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,一定一直练习
Dialogue: 0,1:20:31.58,1:20:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好猛
Dialogue: 0,1:20:34.55,1:20:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我就知道他会赢
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.05,1:20:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.15,1:20:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.66,1:21:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,一个月后，我的英雄羸了
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.36,1:21:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,内藤果然很强
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.88,1:21:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你好，武藤
Dialogue: 0,1:21:17.68,1:21:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,今天好热\N对
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.90,1:21:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那什么\N格斗比赛的票
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.70,1:21:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你要跟太太去吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.70,1:21:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是内藤的吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.25,1:21:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道？
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.75,1:21:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你要跟太太一起去？
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.75,1:21:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,对，怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.71,1:21:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,没有啊
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.16,1:21:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.66,1:22:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,1:22:01.66,1:22:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,1:22:32.80,1:22:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,结束了？\N对
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.70,1:22:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定会赢
Dialogue: 0,1:22:43.65,1:22:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,多亏你了
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.36,1:23:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,一个月没做了
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.51,1:25:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好想舔
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.73,1:27:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢我的肉棒吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.86,1:27:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢
Dialogue: 0,1:27:45.75,1:27:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,这么喜欢啊？
Dialogue: 0,1:27:54.71,1:27:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.68,1:28:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:28:47.40,1:28:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,爽吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:29:09.96,1:29:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:29:24.65,1:29:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,如何？
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.48,1:29:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.91,1:29:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,给你特别服务
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.90,1:29:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,对你使用格斗技
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.00,1:29:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.95,1:30:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,开心吧？\N好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:30:58.80,1:31:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.46,1:31:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.53,1:32:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.06,1:32:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,有被这样过吗？\N没有
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.65,1:32:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.00,1:32:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:32:50.01,1:32:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:33:12.53,1:33:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:34:32.45,1:34:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,想要了？
Dialogue: 0,1:34:39.71,1:34:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,想要吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:34:45.96,1:34:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,操我
Dialogue: 0,1:34:55.56,1:34:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,干什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:34:57.95,1:35:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,又要拍？
Dialogue: 0,1:35:08.81,1:35:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,以前用的面罩
Dialogue: 0,1:35:13.35,1:35:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你竟然记得，对啊
Dialogue: 0,1:35:18.66,1:35:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,戴上去
Dialogue: 0,1:35:21.00,1:35:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,真的？\N对啊
Dialogue: 0,1:35:26.63,1:35:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,真的要戴？好吧
Dialogue: 0,1:35:41.18,1:35:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.58,1:35:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,看我\N好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:35:51.33,1:35:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,认不出来了吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:35:54.10,1:35:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,没有啊
Dialogue: 0,1:35:57.86,1:36:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,转过去
Dialogue: 0,1:36:06.28,1:36:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,趴好
Dialogue: 0,1:36:10.78,1:36:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,继续
Dialogue: 0,1:36:44.71,1:36:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:36:47.18,1:36:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,爽吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.18,1:36:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:37:00.11,1:37:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股翘高
Dialogue: 0,1:37:36.00,1:37:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:38:31.68,1:38:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:39:19.26,1:39:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.40,1:39:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:40:03.65,1:40:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,继续咯
Dialogue: 0,1:40:21.90,1:40:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,继续
Dialogue: 0,1:40:28.10,1:40:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好害羞
Dialogue: 0,1:40:49.90,1:40:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,爽吧？\N好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:41:15.23,1:41:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以，去了
Dialogue: 0,1:41:38.11,1:41:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,去了？
Dialogue: 0,1:41:41.91,1:41:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,过来
Dialogue: 0,1:41:49.05,1:41:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:41:50.61,1:41:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:41:54.50,1:41:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,趴好
Dialogue: 0,1:42:37.43,1:42:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:43:01.23,1:43:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: 0,1:43:29.95,1:43:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: 0,1:43:42.66,1:43:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:43:57.38,1:44:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,自己动
Dialogue: 0,1:44:14.30,1:44:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,继续动
Dialogue: 0,1:44:35.01,1:44:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: 0,1:44:39.48,1:44:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:45:04.11,1:45:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,躺好
Dialogue: 0,1:46:18.68,1:46:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒，去了
Dialogue: 0,1:46:55.83,1:47:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,继续动
Dialogue: 0,1:47:06.86,1:47:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,再来
Dialogue: 0,1:47:59.25,1:48:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,想要吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:48:03.03,1:48:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:49:33.48,1:49:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: 0,1:49:59.91,1:50:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,电话
Dialogue: 0,1:50:03.15,1:50:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不用接啦\N说不定很急
Dialogue: 0,1:50:15.10,1:50:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？\N老公打的
Dialogue: 0,1:50:19.16,1:50:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,接啊\N不可以
Dialogue: 0,1:50:30.80,1:50:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,1:50:32.65,1:50:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,真穗
Dialogue: 0,1:50:35.85,1:50:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么啦？
Dialogue: 0,1:50:37.65,1:50:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我买到票了
Dialogue: 0,1:50:45.45,1:50:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我偷偷买的
Dialogue: 0,1:50:49.01,1:50:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是唷
Dialogue: 0,1:50:50.66,1:50:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那天要空下来喔
Dialogue: 0,1:50:57.30,1:51:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,在东京格斗馆
Dialogue: 0,1:51:02.10,1:51:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我看下几点
Dialogue: 0,1:51:13.78,1:51:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,十一点开始
Dialogue: 0,1:51:19.48,1:51:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,在听吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:51:22.45,1:51:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,有啊
Dialogue: 0,1:51:24.90,1:51:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,在忙吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:51:30.40,1:51:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我很开心，只是很忙
Dialogue: 0,1:51:34.16,1:51:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,等等打给你
Dialogue: 0,1:51:37.26,1:51:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你在干什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:51:40.51,1:51:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我挂了
Dialogue: 0,1:51:53.18,1:51:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,干什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:51:55.90,1:51:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题啦
Dialogue: 0,1:52:00.03,1:52:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,想要吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:52:32.23,1:52:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,1:52:44.00,1:52:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,要疯了
Dialogue: 0,1:53:26.01,1:53:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: 0,1:54:25.20,1:54:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,都说不可以了
Dialogue: 0,1:54:32.28,1:54:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,别拍了
Dialogue: 0,1:54:41.65,1:54:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,1:55:14.28,1:55:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,1:55:15.63,1:55:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,老公，帮忙应门
Dialogue: 0,1:55:18.33,1:55:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,1:55:26.20,1:55:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你好，先生
Dialogue: 0,1:55:30.26,1:55:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,帮我签名
Dialogue: 0,1:55:34.81,1:55:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,太太在家吗？\N对啊
Dialogue: 0,1:55:40.38,1:55:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,1:55:43.15,1:55:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,她很辛苦吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:55:47.21,1:55:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:55:49.33,1:55:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,她常常要去
Dialogue: 0,1:55:53.73,1:55:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,内藤家打扫呢
Dialogue: 0,1:55:56.83,1:55:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道？
Dialogue: 0,1:56:02.80,1:56:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,她说的吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:56:08.78,1:56:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我啊
Dialogue: 0,1:56:13.91,1:56:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,1:56:15.78,1:56:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,快说啊
Dialogue: 0,1:56:20.01,1:56:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么办呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:56:22.03,1:56:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,快说嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:56:25.33,1:56:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,其实
Dialogue: 0,1:56:46.58,1:56:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,内藤其实有个秘密网站
Dialogue: 0,1:56:52.85,1:56:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,里面布满了
Dialogue: 0,1:56:56.86,1:56:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他跟粉丝的性爱影片
Dialogue: 0,1:56:59.60,1:57:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,然后里面一人
Dialogue: 0,1:57:15.28,1:57:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:57:22.65,1:57:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,再来
Dialogue: 0,1:57:27.48,1:57:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,1:57:35.23,1:57:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,在看什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:57:46.51,1:57:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么影片？
Dialogue: 0,1:57:50.21,1:57:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么啦？
Dialogue: 0,1:57:53.88,1:57:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我的妻子
Dialogue: 0,1:57:57.48,1:58:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,被名人上了
Dialogue: 0,1:58:02.93,1:58:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,对方是我的英雄
Dialogue: 0,1:58:05.80,1:58:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,他上了我妻子
